text:
A very big bus stop.
Spacious and windy.
Sheltered to people park complex. Less than 1 minute walk to Chinatown MRT station.
There are so many food stalls, a bubble tea place here and leads you to a mall too.
Normal and typical bus stop in Singapore.
Really good station where you can get to China town easily.
It's a bus stop. Not much different from the others. It's very crowded tho.
